    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine and transmission perform smoothly, and all major systems are fully functional. While the exterior looks great overall, there are some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. This is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate work.",
