    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's ready to hit the road? This vehicle is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a dependable choice for anyone needing practical transportation at a great value. It\u2019s been a faithful companion and is looking for its next adventure!",
